{"tid":851672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲有用單車代步既習慣/經驗","createTime":"2018-10-07T10:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T12:26:54.000Z","uid":68219,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe4542d0902a26b09b02234be014f060f610161","tid":851672,"uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:38:31.000Z","msg":"如題 自己想試下用單車當短中程交通工具用<br />\n本身鍾意中踩單車 識踩 未出過馬路<br />\n驚實行會有好多問題<br />\n最少三個單車鎖帶住行（前轆車身後轆）<br />\n繁忙時間唔好意思搭地鐵（驚整污糟人）<br />\n港島無路行<br />\n唔知買咩款<br />\n<br />\n有好多野都唔知 google又全部都係dse通識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有用既好少<br />\n想聽下過來人經驗 指下路 又過者試過但係放棄咗既巴絲係點諗 趁早點醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8085b417eade0f415c6270d578e589b8bcb9f66","tid":851672,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"揸開林寶代步"},{"pid":"f79987c4ea12a526dd03050f1758236f9f3bc918","tid":851672,"uid":48064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"有時放學會踩共享單車<br />\n次次都踩到出曬水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比著係我踩完之後唔會想做其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非有得沖涼"},{"pid":"c681ba1a2500341541b9d05a5f74358e265fd849","tid":851672,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"點解都踩單車仲要搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27efff314d382069aa8f48d4585814b191df5f9b","tid":851672,"uid":53170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:57:47.000Z","msg":"樓主踩咩地區?<br />\n市區/村郊<br />\n多人/少人<br />\n呢個好重要<br />\n<br />\n利申:當年初中日日踩去補習 買野"},{"pid":"45726b0811ee1c36e3dd62575ae6d586b4b5c279","tid":851672,"uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c681ba1a2